rdf:Description.dct:title: Custodian
rdf:Description.dct:description: Party that accepts accountability and responsibility for the data and ensures appropriate care and maintenance of the resource.

rdf:Description.dct:title: Point of Contact
rdf:Description.dct:description: Party who can be contacted for acquiring knowledge about or acquisition of the resource.

rdf:Description.dct:title: Principal Investigator
rdf:Description.dct:description: Key party responsible for gathering information and conducting research.

rdf:Description.dct:title: Processor
rdf:Description.dct:description: Party who has processed the data in a manner such that the resource has been modified.
